OL,5, Users of Ring video doorbells have     
OL,6, reacted angrily to a huge price hike   
OL,7, being introduced in March.             
OL,9,FAfter buying the devices, customers can
OL,10,Fpay a subscription to store footage on 
OL,11,Fthe cloud, download clips and get      
OL,12,Fdiscounted products.                   
OL,14,FThat subscription is going up 43%, from
OL,15,F#34.99 to #49.99 per device, per year, 
OL,16,Ffor basic plan customers.              
OL,18,FThe firm, which is owned by Amazon,    
OL,19,Finsisted it still provided "some of the
OL,20,Fbest value in the industry."           
